I heard that you raised three children.

41
00:02:11,850 --> 00:02:13,580
Your posture is different for sure.

42
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:15,890
- What did you say? 
 - Food.

43
00:02:15,890 --> 00:02:17,510
Food. Food is here.

44
00:02:17,510 --> 00:02:19,430
- Let's eat food. 
 - Careful.

45
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:21,300
- Hold his head first. 
 - Got it.

46
